						               													<description>A unique print-and-play horror board game for 1-8 players, based on the Frankenstein mythos.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game is for 4-8 players assuming the roles of characters inspired by one of the world&amp;rsquo;s greatest horror stories spanning books and movies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;With this base set, you&amp;rsquo;ll get two different playing experiences as you dive deep into the darkness of an evil-filled world:&amp;#10;The base game for 4-8 players, and a solo-play highly-narrative campaign.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game plays in a maximum of 6 rounds, each one dividen in 3 phases:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Gather, In which you select one of the 6 options to gain resources, with an unique system that allows you to receive resources from adjacent players (you give them resources too).&amp;#10;     Conspire, You will hire a service in one of the 8 available locations (2 possible actions per location), which will be resolved in the next phase (survive).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Interlude: You can reveal your secret character to activate your unique character power and get close to your objective.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Survive, The hired actions resolve in location order, hurting some players, protecting others or giving you that advantage you need to achieve victory.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Reaching the personal goal will cause the end of the game. Some characters may do it during phase 3, others at the end of that phase. The winner will be the person with the most Victory points (reaching the goal will give a gross amount of those sweet points).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
